Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.16,0:24:09.64,title2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)}#15　　马拉松大会 !
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.74,0:00:03.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.11,0:00:06.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为这是平方  所以X是…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.95,0:00:11.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.70,0:00:12.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  接了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.83,0:00:14.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,澪  你现在在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.57,0:00:15.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在家
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.85,0:00:18.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在车站  现在出来一起去玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.95,0:00:22.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…明天开始就是夏季讲习了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.82,0:00:24.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要预习一下才行
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.50,0:00:26.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚上预习不就好了～
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.56,0:00:29.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在玩的话晚上就会很累很困
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.77,0:00:30.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天就不玩了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.80,0:00:33.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎～我和工作哪个比较重要？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.28,0:00:35.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  好了  再见
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.37,0:00:40.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  律什么时候才会学习啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.13,0:00:42.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.29,0:00:44.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.59,0:00:47.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姐现在穿着怎么样的内裤
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.23,0:00:50.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊！啰嗦！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.64,0:00:56.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  该做的事也已经做了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.20,0:00:58.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来该怎么办呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.12,0:01:01.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯也说过要与和一起学习的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.96,0:01:05.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.62,0:01:12.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她要去哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.10,0:01:15.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吓吓她
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.29,0:01:21.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.78,0:01:25.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇～
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.34,0:01:26.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇呀～！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.81,0:01:32.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我发现了小律  所以就想吓吓你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.50,0:01:33.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  败了…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.25,0:01:36.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这种地方能相遇还真稀罕呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.90,0:01:39.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错  你要去哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.96,0:01:41.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从明天开始不就是夏季讲习了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.01,0:01:44.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以就来买些想买的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.70,0:01:45.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.68,0:01:46.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.32,0:01:50.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  没什么  本想你如果有空的话就一起去玩的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.91,0:01:53.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.24,0:01:56.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Just a moment, please
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.21,0:01:56.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要说英语？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.09,0:02:02.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  我是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.82,0:02:05.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天的购物计划能推迟到下次吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.43,0:02:07.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了  拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.98,0:02:10.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有空了  非常空
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.80,0:02:11.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（我说京ani  你不要无预告的换OPED啊  会让我激动地心脏受不了的）
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.28,0:03:48.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至今为止的故事概要
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.53,0:03:51.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的眉毛是腌萝卜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.91,0:03:52.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吃！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.18,0:03:53.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,流口水  
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.09,0:03:56.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,  给我腌萝卜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.55,0:04:00.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就唯一个人吃太狡猾了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.15,0:04:02.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也要吃
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.03,0:04:07.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好…好吃！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.43,0:04:10.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.60,0:04:15.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的两条眉毛都被拿掉的话就会变成稠状物
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.11,0:04:16.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稠状物？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.95,0:04:19.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不快点戴上其它腌萝卜的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.06,0:04:20.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.92,0:04:22.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯  快点把腌萝卜…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.72,0:04:25.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  在这里怎么会有腌萝卜…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.49,0:04:28.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…这种时候  不管是什么都得用用看
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.35,0:04:30.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,治好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.47,0:04:31.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,量角器也行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.84,0:04:34.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三角的东西…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.58,0:04:38.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么我身上会披着毛毯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.20,0:04:41.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只穿一件衣服睡觉的话  会着凉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.90,0:04:44.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在是学习中  应该叫醒我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.66,0:04:46.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那真是对不起了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.84,0:04:50.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那要去哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.68,0:04:53.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交给小律了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.67,0:04:55.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像很高兴啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.53,0:05:00.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我和小律两个人去玩是第一次啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.48,0:05:03.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被你这么一说…确实是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.85,0:05:08.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就带你去你平时不太可能会去的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.80,0:05:10.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如说游戏中心之类的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.33,0:05:12.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,游戏中心…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.64,0:05:14.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  怎么了  没兴趣吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.24,0:05:16.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.61,0:05:18.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想去  很想去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.76,0:05:22.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前和大家一起去的时候玩得很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.07,0:05:23.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧～
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.39,0:05:26.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  那就这么定了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.32,0:05:32.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是游戏中心～
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.02,0:05:34.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是对什么都感动啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.77,0:05:38.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…这个像大吊灯一样闪闪发光的是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.19,0:05:40.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,硬币游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.53,0:05:44.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个装着方向盘的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.67,0:05:45.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赛车游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.13,0:05:48.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里竟然有钓竿
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.57,0:05:49.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是钓鱼游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.97,0:05:51.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎  怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.71,0:05:53.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有趣的东西太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.83,0:05:55.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道该从哪个开始玩了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.10,0:05:56.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷静点
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.34,0:06:00.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  最开始就玩…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.32,0:06:00.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.06,0:06:02.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要玩玩看这个
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.46,0:06:03.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦～
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.68,0:06:07.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也要来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.28,0:06:11.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我为小律报仇了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.29,0:06:13.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.23,0:06:16.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  好想要这个绒毛玩具
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.66,0:06:17.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OK
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.42,0:06:19.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就按这个按钮
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.52,0:06:21.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个  我按
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.30,0:06:28.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可惜
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.52,0:06:29.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.42,0:06:40.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小律好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.05,0:06:42.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.52,0:06:43.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还好抓到了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.87,0:06:47.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  照片OK了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.02,0:06:49.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接着是乱涂鸦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.59,0:06:51.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把这个这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.82,0:06:53.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  这是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.35,0:06:55.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么这个也…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.25,0:06:58.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样也行哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.19,0:07:00.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}Oscar 　{\r}\N奥斯卡～
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.43,0:07:02.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这个按钮吧  我按
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.74,0:07:05.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小律和这个很配哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.90,0:07:07.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是大叔吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.57,0:07:09.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.43,0:07:11.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是猪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.39,0:07:16.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和和的那个好像也很好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.47,0:07:17.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.24,0:07:18.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,换着吃一口吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.71,0:07:21.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  不用了  唯的那个似乎比较贵
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.73,0:07:23.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系啦  我也想吃吃看你的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.14,0:07:25.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗  那么就…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.14,0:07:34.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和和…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.27,0:07:36.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.98,0:07:40.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  玩得好开心～
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.30,0:07:43.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能这么开心就不枉我带你去了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.82,0:07:46.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我太开心了  明天说不定会死
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.89,0:07:48.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会不会不会不会
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.58,0:07:50.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是用了不少钱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.19,0:07:53.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是接下来就得节约着…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.13,0:07:55.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去粗点店逛一圈吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.69,0:08:00.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,粗点店…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.35,0:08:02.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小律…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.40,0:08:02.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.35,0:08:05.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱…抱一抱你行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.35,0:08:06.48,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（よか：よい的九州方言）
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.44,0:08:06.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是哪里人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.76,0:08:11.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这  这就是粗点店？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.47,0:08:14.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错  这里的东西每一个都只要20到30日元
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.11,0:08:16.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以可以不用顾虑尽情地买
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.42,0:08:18.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.03,0:08:19.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个也是？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.89,0:08:20.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个也是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.80,0:08:22.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个串起来的东西也是？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.75,0:08:23.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.55,0:08:25.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个像油炸食物一样的东西也是？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.50,0:08:25.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.31,0:08:28.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么大的仙贝也是？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.24,0:08:28.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.27,0:08:32.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害  难道说价格破坏就是指这个？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.27,0:08:32.73,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（价格破坏：出自作家城山三郎的同名书籍「価格破壊」，\N讲述主角以低价商品起家的商业斗争）
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.83,0:08:33.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得不是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.92,0:08:39.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在吃粗点时  有着各种各样的技巧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.33,0:08:42.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如说要打开膨化棒的话  就要这样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.49,0:08:43.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.19,0:08:49.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有  要喝这个的话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.87,0:08:50.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从这头开始
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.07,0:08:51.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.58,0:08:56.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从这头开始喝的话  就能一点点喝  喝的时间也就长了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.30,0:08:57.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗  好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.24,0:08:59.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.62,0:09:01.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.94,0:09:05.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个要这样搅在一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.00,0:09:06.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后吃
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.05,0:09:09.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.73,0:09:10.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.19,0:09:12.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蛋糕上的草莓？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.68,0:09:14.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然就吃掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.86,0:09:16.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种事我不知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.04,0:09:19.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很奇怪吧  一般不会这样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.75,0:09:22.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？没什么不明白的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.95,0:09:25.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看吧  并不是什么奇怪的事情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.86,0:09:29.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是最容易拿的  而且吃蛋糕部分又觉得不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.19,0:09:34.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对啊  蛋糕上的草莓是蛋糕的顶点  心脏  灵魂
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.74,0:09:36.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是唯这么想的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.37,0:09:38.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对  全世界都是这样认为的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.65,0:09:39.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是姐姐打来的？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.11,0:09:41.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真拿你没办法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.87,0:09:43.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我把我的栗子给你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.13,0:09:45.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样就扯平了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.33,0:09:47.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  不对～
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.51,0:09:49.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梓喵  很奇怪是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.30,0:09:51.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是和和错了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.60,0:09:55.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊～玩得太开心了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.01,0:09:57.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.39,0:10:01.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小律真是知道很多我不知道的东西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.40,0:10:02.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.22,0:10:04.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再多多表扬我吧～
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.11,0:10:06.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用500日元就拿到了这个
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.12,0:10:09.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用100日元就吃得饱饱了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.11,0:10:13.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小律真是不用钱就能玩的达人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.53,0:10:18.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  但对于一般人来说今天花的钱已经很多了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.50,0:10:20.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.67,0:10:21.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.84,0:10:23.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老实说上个月也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.09,0:10:32.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思  澪  能稍微借我一点钱吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.27,0:10:34.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又要吗  差多少…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.51,0:10:36.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶  要借给我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.30,0:10:41.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么就再追加这个鼓棒和新总谱  还有昨天发卖的新CD
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.54,0:10:42.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天都买了行吗～
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.95,0:10:47.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后澪很过分啊  突然就给了我一拳
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.41,0:10:49.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一拳…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.01,0:10:54.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.26,0:10:58.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实有件事想要拜托小律…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.05,0:11:00.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,钱的话我没有哦～
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.00,0:11:01.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.65,0:11:04.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…不是的  我不是那个意思
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.34,0:11:10.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有件事我从很久以前就一直很憧憬…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.77,0:11:11.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,憧憬？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.11,0:11:12.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.35,0:11:19.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  希望你能打我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.59,0:11:22.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.58,0:11:27.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啥？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.24,0:11:31.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,K-ON!!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.02,0:11:35.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐  到时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.18,0:11:40.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天要去夏季讲习吧？该起床…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.64,0:11:44.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  已经起来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.52,0:11:49.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…好久没用闹钟  结果设早了一个小时
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.40,0:11:57.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不小心穿着校服来了  怎么办…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.44,0:11:58.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  校服！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.58,0:12:04.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难…难道夏季讲习要穿校服吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.59,0:12:09.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…这种时候穿校服才比较正常吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.54,0:12:11.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  这样？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.63,0:12:12.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.42,0:12:14.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  唯你竟然这么早就来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.65,0:12:19.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小律怎么办  夏季讲习好像要穿校服来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.32,0:12:22.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  没这回事吧  你看
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.38,0:12:23.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的哎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.64,0:12:27.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒是见不到几个穿校服的人呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.03,0:12:31.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果只有澪一个人的话该怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.29,0:12:36.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「快看快看～只有那个人穿校服来上课诶」
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.70,0:12:37.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗬嗬嗬～
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.69,0:12:38.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,够了！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.85,0:12:42.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然说了穿什么都行那就没关系吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.24,0:12:43.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.64,0:12:48.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,换衣服花了不少时间
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.09,0:12:50.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早…早
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.20,0:12:53.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿得像去海边时一样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.95,0:12:57.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  难道说上完课大家要去海边…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.29,0:12:58.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…没那回事儿
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.74,0:12:59.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.16,0:13:04.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下  
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.43,0:13:06.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.33,0:13:08.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,标签还没拿掉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.15,0:13:12.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有你这身衣服不要穿短袜比较好看
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.26,0:13:19.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  难不成是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.11,0:13:22.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望你能打我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.35,0:13:25.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说  挨打只会疼的…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.56,0:13:27.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我也希望你可以打我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.63,0:13:30.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要说到这份上我也无所谓…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.82,0:13:31.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.27,0:13:33.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轻轻来一下就行了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.25,0:13:35.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托您了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.52,0:13:39.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…周围没什么保镖吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.28,0:13:41.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有那种东西
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.61,0:13:43.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.99,0:13:44.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.96,0:13:50.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…我就手刀吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.51,0:13:51.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请随意！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.15,0:14:01.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行  打不下去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.98,0:14:02.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.70,0:14:04.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然说打你也敲不下去啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.86,0:14:06.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种事情要看时机
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.86,0:14:07.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时机？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.11,0:14:08.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.97,0:14:11.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么都没做就来打你太说不过去了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.94,0:14:13.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是捅个大篓子什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.04,0:14:16.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自然就会有人跳出来说事儿了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.39,0:14:17.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,捅个大篓子…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.20,0:14:20.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧  和和很奇怪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.74,0:14:24.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说可以尝一口  可一般也不会吃那里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.62,0:14:25.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难不成是想…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.49,0:14:26.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  应该是闹着玩的吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.06,0:14:31.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前律抢走我的草莓的时候  我还打过她
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.96,0:14:33.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以能理解啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.28,0:14:36.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和和很自然地就吃掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.88,0:14:36.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对没错了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.62,0:14:42.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之先去看看参考书吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.22,0:14:46.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有没有什么书吃了就能变聪明呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.68,0:14:45.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,  来这边
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.20,0:14:47.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有才怪了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.81,0:14:50.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你果然是准备好来闹笑话的么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.72,0:14:51.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样不行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.55,0:14:56.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得这算是最不配夏季讲习的衣服了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.11,0:15:00.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉实在是微妙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.81,0:15:04.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种事情要做得简单明了才行
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.18,0:15:07.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小澪  好热哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.67,0:15:08.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,废话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.93,0:15:09.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.96,0:15:10.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么好记的！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.26,0:15:14.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒是你就那么想被人打一次吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.38,0:15:18.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  因为小律和小澪每次看上去都那么亲密
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.58,0:15:16.72,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我注意一点
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.89,0:15:18.19,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别这样～
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.43,0:15:21.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯和小梓也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.78,0:15:24.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总感觉我没有那种亲密对象
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.88,0:15:26.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人家明明很喜欢亲密的说
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.95,0:15:29.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  已经很粘人了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.90,0:15:33.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行  你都说到这份上了我就帮你一把
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.16,0:15:34.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.20,0:15:37.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出来耍宝就不要怕丢脸！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.45,0:15:40.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,耍就要给他耍个大的！明白？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.25,0:15:41.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.51,0:15:46.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过没想到唯和律都决定升学
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.39,0:15:51.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为小佐和说现在去找工作的话实在是太晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.63,0:15:54.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算现在备考也真不算早了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.36,0:15:56.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  头巾
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.34,0:15:57.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.17,0:15:58.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.09,0:15:59.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,澪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.14,0:16:00.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.06,0:16:03.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我准备明年再战！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.22,0:16:05.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别闹了你！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.36,0:16:06.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小澪  我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.41,0:16:10.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,  好合适哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.27,0:16:10.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.11,0:16:12.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你戴一般的眼镜有什么用啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.97,0:16:17.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太耀眼了我看不下去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.96,0:16:23.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯你看  只要眯起眼睛  文章中间就会有文字显现出来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.14,0:16:25.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  看到了！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.31,0:16:26.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是「A」  是「A」啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.95,0:16:27.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看得到就有鬼了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.09,0:16:30.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.45,0:16:33.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根据文脉来看  答案是…A！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.75,0:16:34.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.85,0:16:37.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,认真解答不行的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.82,0:16:39.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思  没注意…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.37,0:16:41.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请收好这张卡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.91,0:16:46.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我应该带照的好看的照片来才是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.14,0:16:48.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的就挺好的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.29,0:16:51.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是个比较缩的人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.23,0:16:53.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别在这里乱来！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.59,0:16:54.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  ！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.71,0:16:55.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.52,0:16:56.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的是这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.22,0:16:59.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好！这次一定行！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.75,0:17:03.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊  你们都是贴上去的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.35,0:17:05.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,半睁的眼…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.68,0:17:08.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正常的怎么可以更有冲击力啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.14,0:17:08.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.93,0:17:09.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看  看
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.01,0:17:10.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你妹！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.83,0:17:13.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿嘿  交上去的照片拿错了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.04,0:17:16.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然天然呆的新鲜度是不一样的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.74,0:17:17.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.36,0:17:20.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全力…明明都用尽全力了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.11,0:17:23.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道咱们很拼啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.51,0:17:26.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过怎么说呢  就是感觉很难下手
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.67,0:17:29.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,澪对上你的话又有点那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.83,0:17:31.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果还是行不通的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.07,0:17:33.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.57,0:17:35.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的  久等啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.46,0:17:35.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.95,0:17:37.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回家啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.07,0:17:41.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天是返校日  你还记得吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.87,0:17:45.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然记得啦  好久没见到大家了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.19,0:17:47.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.48,0:17:53.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蛋糕多了一份…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.77,0:17:56.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个要分成五等份很困难啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.48,0:17:57.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就猜拳
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.83,0:18:00.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦…我猜拳很弱  不要
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.32,0:18:04.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好  那就用这个来决定吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.32,0:18:04.06,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（指スマ（指SMA）：名字出自SMAP×SMAP发售的同名游戏，报数人报出的\N数字和竖起的拇指数相同则胜利脱出队伍 ，依次进行到只剩一人时游戏结束）
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.35,0:18:07.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧  我接受挑战
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.96,0:18:11.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  那谁赢了谁拿蛋糕
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.37,0:18:13.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,垫底的每人赏她一下额头
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.90,0:18:14.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  弹额头？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.04,0:18:16.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  来吧来吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.47,0:18:17.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,输掉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.51,0:18:19.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,输掉就能被捶一次了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.57,0:18:20.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.81,0:18:22.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  准备了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.44,0:18:24.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从我开始  准备  5！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.26,0:18:26.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准备  3！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.68,0:18:27.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.91,0:18:29.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准备  7！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.22,0:18:30.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准备  1！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.67,0:18:31.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准备  2！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.99,0:18:34.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成了！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.70,0:18:41.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提案的人输掉了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.16,0:18:43.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.02,0:18:45.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎…嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.80,0:18:48.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  赶紧吃完去练习吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.65,0:18:53.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  今天有草莓吃  没什么好抱怨的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.18,0:18:58.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前律抢走我的草莓的时候  我还打过她
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.42,0:19:18.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和和！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.27,0:19:20.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了  唯？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.22,0:19:22.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.39,0:19:24.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,草莓被抢走了  澪在伤心啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.70,0:19:28.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,澪在哭泣啊！草莓就是这么重要的东西啊！和和！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.52,0:19:31.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原…原来我真是做了件坏事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.05,0:19:34.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你终于理解了  和和
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.01,0:19:36.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小澪  抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.69,0:19:38.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想被打一次？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.02,0:19:41.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  都怪我任性
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.90,0:19:45.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对  捅那么大一篓子  澪一点反应都没有才是问题！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.94,0:19:46.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不对吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.43,0:19:50.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的话  早点和我们讲不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.55,0:19:52.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是轻轻打一次对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.29,0:19:54.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可…可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.94,0:19:56.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打一下也不会怎么样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.12,0:19:58.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可以抱一抱你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.07,0:20:00.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又来了  你是哪里人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.02,0:20:03.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.75,0:20:05.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…你真怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.08,0:20:07.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.57,0:20:18.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉…好紧张呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.09,0:20:22.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…为什么是我？！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.71,0:20:27.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到头还是不顺利啊  抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.70,0:20:30.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？不  该道歉的应该是我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.89,0:20:32.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求你做这种怪事情
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.85,0:20:36.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是想被打一下的话  肯定有什么办法的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.04,0:20:38.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如说…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.44,0:20:40.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢  不过已经无所谓了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.91,0:20:41.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.22,0:20:45.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  你额头好红
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.98,0:20:51.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小律你真的很擅长帮助别人哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.30,0:20:53.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.40,0:20:57.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心地善良  为了帮助别人又不辞辛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.28,0:21:00.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是男生的话  一定很受欢迎吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.47,0:21:01.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.88,0:21:07.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你叫我说什么好啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.74,0:21:08.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好疼～
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.72,0:21:15.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  就是这样  抱歉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.55,0:21:20.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看  前几日不是打电话找你出来玩吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.65,0:21:21.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后来就遇到了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.58,0:21:24.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  你问去哪儿了？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.81,0:21:27.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…粗点店和游戏中心之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.65,0:21:32.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙看什么都觉得新鲜
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.56,0:21:34.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她倒是一直这样啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.86,0:21:38.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后她就说好想被打一次
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.84,0:21:42.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种事情要看时机吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.52,0:21:45.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我呢…喂？澪？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.20,0:21:49.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  你难道…生气了？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.33,0:21:50.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.18,0:21:50.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.08,0:21:53.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你当时为什么不找我出来啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.16,0:21:56.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想和出去玩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.48,0:21:59.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是找你了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.48,0:23:44.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都度过了一个充实的暑假吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.87,0:23:50.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能久违地看到大家晒黑后充满精神的面容
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.51,0:23:53.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也觉得十分高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.64,0:23:56.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在高中生的暑假里获得的经验…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.13,0:24:02.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要跑42.195公里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.63,0:24:03.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可思议的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.98,0:24:05.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错  就是这个
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.13,0:24:07.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的话马拉松大会就会中止
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.11,0:24:09.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,变成甜豆汤大会！


